#: app.py:108
msgid "Loading... Keep your cursor steady."
msgstr "正在加载中……手不要抖。"

#: app.py:109
msgid "PP has gone."
msgstr "PP 飞走了。"

#: app.py:110
msgid "Attempting to parse a 400pp jump map..."
msgstr "正在尝试解析一张 400pp 的跳图……"

#: app.py:111
msgid "Who moved my mouse sensitivity?"
msgstr "谁动了我的鼠标灵敏度？"

#: app.py:112
msgid "Don’t take it too seriously, this is just a toy."
msgstr "别太较真，这只是个玩具。"

#: app.py:113
msgid "Re-timing the map... No wait, it’s perfectly aligned this time!"
msgstr "对齐时轴中……已经对齐了！"

#: app.py:114
msgid "I've got a slider break!"
msgstr "我断滑条了！"

#: app.py:115
msgid "Shh, don’t tell anyone what this tool is built with."
msgstr "嘘，别和其他人说这个工具是用什么构建的。"

#: app.py:116
msgid "Calculating how long your wrist can last."
msgstr "正在计算你的手腕还能坚持多久。"

#: app.py:117
msgid "This loading bar moves slower than a 128-BPM song."
msgstr "这进度条动得比 128 BPM 的歌还慢。"

#: app.py:118
msgid ""
"Tip: You can nod your head to the beat even if the loading bar is stuck."
msgstr "小贴士：即使进度条不动，你也可以跟着节奏点头。"

#: app.py:119
msgid "I want a rhythm-pulsing progress bar like Lazer’s."
msgstr "我想要一个 Lazer 同款跟随节奏律动的进度条。"

#: app.py:120
msgid "Pooling is a headache."
msgstr "选图真令人头疼。"

#: app.py:121
msgid "Loading Stellar Railway... Wait, I meant star rating."
msgstr "正在启动星……啊不对，加载星数。"

#: app.py:122
msgid "My ACC is expanding and contracting with temperature."
msgstr "我的准确率正在热胀冷缩。"

#: app.py:123
msgid "Generating fake SS screenshots..."
msgstr "正在生成虚假的 SS 截图。"

#: app.py:124
msgid "Loading miss hitsound... 404 Not Found."
msgstr "正在加载 miss 击打音效…… 404 你访问的页面不存在。"

#: app.py:125
msgid "Why is your HP thicker than MMORPG bosses?"
msgstr "你的血条怎么比大型多人在线角色扮演游戏的头目还厚？"

#: app.py:126
msgid "I'm not a fan of DT."
msgstr "我不喜欢 DT。"

#: app.py:127
msgid "Calculating how much patience you need..."
msgstr "正在计算你需要多少耐心……"

#: app.py:128
msgid "Loading \"my hand slipped\" excuse generator..."
msgstr "正在加载“我手滑了”借口生成器……"

#: app.py:129
msgid "Generating fake \"this is my first time playing\" claims..."
msgstr "正在编造“这是我第一次玩”的谎言……"

#: app.py:130
msgid "Loading C#, Rust, JavaScript and so on..."
msgstr "正在加载 C#、Rust、JavaScript 等……"

#: app.py:131
msgid "Calculating how much time you have wasted..."
msgstr "正在计算你已经浪费了多少时间……"

#: app.py:132
msgid "Sleeping..."
msgstr "睡觉中……"

#: app.py:133
msgid "Refactoring spaghetti code? No, just piling it up."
msgstr "重构屎山代码？不不不，堆叠屎山代码。"

#: app.py:134
msgid ""
"If you see this tip for more than 5 seconds, the thread is probably dead."
msgstr "如果这条小贴士显示超过 5 秒钟，线程可能已经死了。"

#: app.py:135
msgid "There are no bugs, only undocumented features."
msgstr "没有 bug，只有未标明特性。"

#: app.py:136
msgid "The loading bar is actually of random length, stop staring at it."
msgstr "进度条是随机的，别盯着它了。"

#: app.py:137
#, python-format
msgid "If I told you it were 99%% loaded, would you believe me?"
msgstr "如果我说已经加载了 99%% 了，你会信吗？"

#: app.py:138
msgid "Analyzing your play history... it seems you like Tech maps?"
msgstr "正在分析你的游玩历史……似乎你喜欢 Tech 图？"

#: app.py:139
msgid "Stop looking at the Accuracy, enjoy the music!"
msgstr "别关注准确率了，享受音乐！"

#: app.py:140
msgid "Loading... (This tip is also part of the loading process)"
msgstr "正在加载中……（是的，仅此而已）"

#: app.py:143
msgid "Loading necessary objects..."
msgstr "正在加载必要对象……"

#: app.py:162
msgid "Please click the button below to authorize the app."
msgstr "请点击下方的按钮以完成授权。"

#: app.py:163
msgid "OAuth2 URL"
msgstr "授权链接"

